    SELECT DISTINCT [a].[IPN_Id], [a].[IPN_No], [a].[IPN_Date], [a].[IPN_StuStaffFlg], [a].[IPN_PushNotification], [c].[AMST_Id], [b].[HRME_Id], (((CASE
        WHEN [e].[AMST_FirstName] IS NULL
        THEN N' ' ELSE [e].[AMST_FirstName]
    END + N' ') + CASE
        WHEN [e].[AMST_MiddleName] IS NULL
        THEN N' ' ELSE [e].[AMST_MiddleName]
    END) + N' ') + CASE

    SELECT DISTINCT [a].[IPN_Id], [a].[IPN_No], [a].[IPN_Date], [a].[IPN_StuStaffFlg], [a].[IPN_PushNotification], [c].[AMST_Id], [b].[HRME_Id], (((CASE
        WHEN [e].[AMST_FirstName] IS NULL
        THEN N' ' ELSE [e].[AMST_FirstName]
    END + N' ') + CASE
        WHEN [e].[AMST_MiddleName] IS NULL
        THEN N' ' ELSE [e].[AMST_MiddleName]

    CROSS JOIN [IVRM_PushNotification_Staff] AS [b]
    CROSS JOIN [IVRM_PushNotification_Student] AS [c]
    CROSS JOIN [HR_Master_Employee] AS [d]
